data.title: they have a great selection of International foods
data.text:
I have there many times as a shopper. I buy sardines from Morocco, beets and sauerkraut from Poland . the beets and
sauerkraut are the best I have eaten in a long time. The brand 
is Zergut. there is much to shop for. Give it a try.
There is a deli, where the woman prepares ethnic dishes.
All well prepared,
